---
import Container from "../ui/Container.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../ui/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section class="story">

  <Container>

    <div class="story-grid">

      <div>

        <SectionHeader
          eyebrow="OUR STORY"
          title="Three Decades of Manufacturing Excellence"
        />

      </div>

      <div class="content">

        <p>
          Established in <strong>1997</strong>, S R Group began with a clear
          vision—to manufacture quality chemical products while building
          relationships founded on trust, consistency and integrity.
        </p>

        <p>
          Over the years, the group has expanded into multiple manufacturing
          companies, serving industries across India with dependable products,
          technical expertise and a customer-first approach.
        </p>

        <p>
          Today, S R Group comprises
          <strong>S R Industries</strong>,
          <strong>S R Plast</strong> and
          <strong>S R Polymers</strong>,
          combining decades of manufacturing experience with continuous
          investment in quality, infrastructure and innovation.
        </p>

        <p>
          While our operations have grown, our philosophy remains unchanged —
          deliver consistent quality, honour commitments and build long-term
          partnerships with every customer.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </Container>

</section>

<style>

.story{
padding:7rem 0;
}

.story-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1.35fr;
gap:6rem;
align-items:start;
}

.content{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:2rem;
}

.content p{
margin:0;
font-size:1.08rem;
line-height:1.95;
color:var(--color-text-light);
}

.content strong{
color:var(--color-primary);
font-weight:600;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.story-grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
gap:3rem;
}

.story{
padding:5rem 0;
}

}

</style>
